body: Passed out from overstimulation and lack of oxygen. She ain't dead, but her frigging idiot brother should give her a break or she will be.
That got dark, hope this isnt the end

Definitely the most hardcore chapter of the series. Kinda miffed about the fact that we don't see them talking about it beforehand like we usually do. It probably was her idea but I would have preferred it if she was shown to have more agency in this one
